Our Team

The Research Park is managed by a tight-knit team that facilitates resources for tenants and cultivates community among employees. These University of Illinois professionals work on the continued development and growth of the companies within Research Park and the EnterpriseWorks incubator. 

Not sure who to contact? Email research-park@illinois.edu and we’ll be sure to route your question to the right person.
